snippet.title: The Exit 8 VR | Teaser Trailer | Meta Quest Platform
snippet.description:
Make sure not to overlook any anomalies.

If you find any anomalies, turn back immediately.

If you don't find any anomalies, keep going.

Kindly exit through Exit 8.

The Exit 8 VR is a short walking simulator inspired by Japanese underground passageways, liminal spaces and back rooms.

The acclaimed indie sensation is coming soon on Meta Quest, for an even more immersive experience.


Pre-order now on the Quest Store!
⏬Meta Quest Store⏬
https://metaque.st/4eaWxsE
